OL,3,CFormer Bristol Mayor Marvin Rees and
OL,4,Cex-Bristol MP given peerages
OL,6,FFormer Bristol Mayor Marvin Rees and
OL,7,Fex-Bristol Labour MP Thangam
OL,8,FDebbonaire have been awarded life
OL,9,Fpeerages by the Prime Minister and are
OL,10,Fset to enter the House of Lords.
OL,12,FThe political nominations were
OL,13,Fannounced on Friday 20 December by
OL,14,FNumber 10 Downing Street and include
OL,15,F30 Labour ennoblements, six Tories and
OL,16,Fseven Liberal Democrats.
