OL,3,CFormer Bristol Mayor Marvin Rees and
OL,4,Cex-Bristol MP given peerages
OL,6,FMr Rees served as the second and final
OL,7,FBristol Mayor from 2016 until 2024,
OL,8,Fand in his leaving speech cited
OL,9,Fhousing in the city as one of his
OL,10,Fgreatest achievements.
OL,12,FIn 2023, he failed in a bid to stand
OL,13,Fas the Labour Party's candidate in the
OL,14,Fnew constituency of Bristol North
OL,15,FEast, which was won by former
OL,16,FKingswood MP Damien Egan.
