OL,3,CFormer Bristol Mayor Marvin Rees and
OL,4,Cex-Bristol MP given peerages
OL,6,FAfter ending his term as Mayor - a
OL,7,Frole abolished by the electorate
OL,8,Fduring local elections of 2022 - Mr
OL,9,FRees was appointed as a professor at
OL,10,Fthe University of Bristol's
OL,11,Fenvironmental department.
OL,13,FHis time in office was not short of
OL,14,Fcontroversy, with journalists
OL,15,Fboycotting formal mayoral briefings in
OL,16,F2022 after he said local democracy
OL,17,Freporters were "not invited".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
