OL,3,CFormer Bristol Mayor Marvin Rees and
OL,4,Cex-Bristol MP given peerages
OL,6,FThe comments followed a clip in which
OL,7,Fa local reporter asked during a
OL,8,Fbriefing if Mr Rees "saw the irony" in
OL,9,Fflying to Vancouver to deliver a talk
OL,10,Fon climate change. The then Bristol
OL,11,FMayor denied there was ever a ban on
OL,12,FLDRs joining his briefings.
