OL,3,CFormer Bristol Mayor Marvin Rees and
OL,4,Cex-Bristol MP given peerages
OL,6,FMs Debbonaire, who represented Bristol
OL,7,FWest from 2015 until 2024, missed out
OL,8,Fon a role in Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,9,Fcabinet after she was beaten by the
OL,10,FGreen Party's Carla Denyer to take the
OL,11,Fnew Bristol Central seat in July.
OL,12,FBefore the election, she had one of
OL,13,FLabour's largest parliamentary
OL,14,Fmajorities.
OL,16,FHaving been on Labour's front bench,
OL,17,FMs Debbonaire was widely tipped to
OL,18,Fbecome the new Culture Secretary.
