OL,3,CFormer Bristol Mayor Marvin Rees and
OL,4,Cex-Bristol MP given peerages
OL,6,FOn receiving a peerage, she said on X:
OL,7,F"I'm honoured to be asked to join the
OL,8,FHouse of Lords. I'm grateful to the
OL,9,FPrime Minister for giving me this
OL,10,Fopportunity to serve the country and
OL,11,Fsupport the Labour government he leads
OL,12,Fto transform the UK."
OL,14,FThe two Bristol politicians join Keir
OL,15,FStarmer's former chief of staff, Sue
OL,16,FGray, in being awarded the lifetime
OL,17,Fpeerages.
